&lt;CIIT Inc> said it filed a finalprospectus for a 15 mln dlr rights offering to subscribe for1.1 mln common shares at 13.85 dlrs each.    Under the terms of the offering, each common share holderwill receive 1-1/2 rights for each common share held on March13 and each right will entitle the holder to subscribe for onecommon share at 13.85 dlrs each by April 13, the company said. Reuter&#3;